INSERT INTO `cms_article_content` VALUES ('9040','<p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">转眼间6月份即将结束，买车君认为这个月对汽车行业来说具有独特的历史意义。6月6日，国家发改委表示严禁各地出台新的汽车限购规定，对新能源汽车实行的限行限购应当取消；6月24日，工信部宣布取消在业内存在4年之久的新能源汽车动力电池“白名单”；6月25日，新能源汽车的补贴过渡期正式结束，新补贴政策会正式上线。</p><p><img src=\"http://p1.pstatp.com/large/pgc-image/4b5b725fa1f74d13a8a156e0507e6d5d\" img_width=\"1080\" img_height=\"719\" alt=\"恐慌中，最严国六和新购置税法将在下周共同实施\" inline=\"0\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; border-style: none; max-width: 100%; display: block; margin: 10px auto;\"/></p><p class=\"pgc-img-caption\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); line-height: 16px;\"><br/></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">与6月相比，7月份也同样不简单。因为从7月1日起，汽车行业将又有一些新规开始实施，如果你接下来准备买车，不妨先了解一下。</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">国六排放标准</span></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">国六排放标准大家都有所了解，本来该政策全国全面实施时间设定在2020年7月，但在巨大的环境压力下，全国有十余个省市将国六排放标准提前到2019年7月1日起实施。一旦“国六”开始执行，车企出厂销售的车辆，必须满足国六排放标准，不符合排放标准的车辆将被禁止销售、注册和转入。</p><p><img src=\"http://p3.pstatp.com/large/pgc-image/1a1e5d6d318c49de9ad2dccb4281b9c6\" img_width=\"961\" img_height=\"693\" alt=\"恐慌中，最严国六和新购置税法将在下周共同实施\" inline=\"0\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; border-style: none; max-width: 100%; display: block; margin: 10px auto;\"/></p><p class=\"pgc-img-caption\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); line-height: 16px;\"><br/></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">这次虽然提前实施的只有十余个城市，但它们的影响力却不小，因为这些城市的销量占全国乘用车市场的60%-70%，也不难理解为何车企们都那么紧张。作为目前世界上最严格的排放标准之一，要让发动机符合“国六”也并非易事，它不仅有技术门槛要求，也有成本上涨压力，这对于那些尚未做足准备功课的车企来说确实是个不小的考验。</p><p><img src=\"http://p1.pstatp.com/large/pgc-image/6257c34acc3d49a585e9cecdb8234fd8\" img_width=\"1080\" img_height=\"610\" alt=\"恐慌中，最严国六和新购置税法将在下周共同实施\" inline=\"0\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; border-style: none; max-width: 100%; display: block; margin: 10px auto;\"/></p><p class=\"pgc-img-caption\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); line-height: 16px;\"><br/></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">据买车君了解，目前合资品牌基本都有国六车型在售。但各品牌的节奏不一，有些品牌只是少数几款车型有国六版本，有些品牌的所有主力车型均完成了国六排放的切换。以上汽通用旗下三大品牌为例，在提前实施国六标准的地区已基本做到全系产品满足国六b，尤其1.3T+ CVT为代表的第八代Ecotec发动机系列，应用Smart propulsion智驱科技，一步到位满足国六b，动力油耗表现进一步优化升级，更具市场竞争力。</p><p><img src=\"http://p1.pstatp.com/large/pgc-image/f4933f7e6b2146199ee035ab3030f7b9\" img_width=\"1080\" img_height=\"810\" alt=\"恐慌中，最严国六和新购置税法将在下周共同实施\" inline=\"0\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; border-style: none; max-width: 100%; display: block; margin: 10px auto;\"/></p><p class=\"pgc-img-caption\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); line-height: 16px;\"><br/></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">如果大部分车企的车型都无法推出国六版本，那消费者将是该政策的受害者。首先，他们近期将会面临可选车型减少的局面，买车君从机动车环保网统计的国六车型目录中查询发现，目前已经有超过400款的国六车型登上目录，但仍有十多家企业尚未有任何一款国六车型在列。这也意味着7月份之后，那些没有国六车型的品牌将陷入无车可卖的尴尬境地，而消费者可选车型的范围也会缩小。</p><p><img src=\"http://p1.pstatp.com/large/pgc-image/139e34cbd4624a17ba703124250d0f21\" img_width=\"1080\" img_height=\"664\" alt=\"恐慌中，最严国六和新购置税法将在下周共同实施\" inline=\"0\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; border-style: none; max-width: 100%; display: block; margin: 10px auto;\"/></p><p class=\"pgc-img-caption\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); line-height: 16px;\"><br/></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">同时，如果你是个大排量发动机的忠实拥趸，在执行国六标准后很有可能你要“忍痛割爱”，因为很多大排量的进口车都达不到国六排放标准，类似野马、陆地巡洋舰、途乐都会受此波及。</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">更关键的是，相同车型的国六版本会比国五版本的售价要高，毕竟国五到国六在技术升级上也有成本增加。即使个别车型官方售价不变，但终端优惠也没以往那么多。总之，如果不急于用车，可以静观一段时间，后期买国六车型会更合算一些。</p><p><img src=\"http://p1.pstatp.com/large/pgc-image/803976435e6a449288b82630243503f0\" img_width=\"1080\" img_height=\"100\" alt=\"恐慌中，最严国六和新购置税法将在下周共同实施\" inline=\"0\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; border-style: none; max-width: 100%; display: block; margin: 10px auto;\"/></p><p class=\"pgc-img-caption\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); line-height: 16px;\"><br/></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">总的来说，国六排放标准的实施虽然给车企带来了不少难题，也增加了消费者的购车成本。但是，国六排放标准的到来，无论是对汽车行业的未来发展，还是对整个人类出行环境来说都是百益而无一害的。</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">新汽车购置税法</span></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">除了国六之外，新汽车购置税法也将在2019年7月1日实施，税率为10%。新政策下的购置税法，最明显的变化是计税的依据，此前是根据厂商指导价或者开具的发票金额进行计算，现在则是根据新车的成交价格来计算。</p><p><img src=\"http://p3.pstatp.com/large/pgc-image/bd046ea837314bf19500fbf5a6319a4e\" img_width=\"1080\" img_height=\"719\" alt=\"恐慌中，最严国六和新购置税法将在下周共同实施\" inline=\"0\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; border-style: none; max-width: 100%; display: block; margin: 10px auto;\"/></p><p class=\"pgc-img-caption\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); line-height: 16px;\"><br/></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">举个简单的例子，如果一辆官方指导价为20万元的车型，现在有3万元的终端优惠。在7月1日以前，按照官方指导价申报计税价格，消费者所需缴纳的购置税为20万÷（1+13%）×10%=17699元。而在7月1日以后，按照实际的购买价格申报计税价格，那么购置税为17万÷（1+13%）×10%=15044元，相比旧政策消费者节省了2655元。</p><p><img src=\"http://p1.pstatp.com/large/pgc-image/280203fb78d24ac99403696df184de0c\" img_width=\"1080\" img_height=\"608\" alt=\"恐慌中，最严国六和新购置税法将在下周共同实施\" inline=\"0\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; border-style: none; max-width: 100%; display: block; margin: 10px auto;\"/></p><p class=\"pgc-img-caption\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); line-height: 16px;\"><br/></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">不过，政府为了防止偷税漏税，也针对每款车型的购置税设定一个最低征收额，即便购车发票金额远低于市场平均价格，也要按照最低征收额来缴税。当然，如果你是加价提车，那么计税价格则要算上加价的金额，所缴纳的购置税自然也就更高了。</p><p><img src=\"http://p3.pstatp.com/large/pgc-image/f60a9a3187c44fd488c02ac77a6e70c3\" img_width=\"1080\" img_height=\"810\" alt=\"恐慌中，最严国六和新购置税法将在下周共同实施\" inline=\"0\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; border-style: none; max-width: 100%; display: block; margin: 10px auto;\"/></p><p class=\"pgc-img-caption\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); line-height: 16px;\"><br/></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">同时，新政还提到了退车可申请退还购置税。比如某车主买了一辆20万元的车型，缴纳的购置税为17699元。在使用了1年以后，由于某种原因与车企协商退车，那么可以申请退还的购置税为17699×（1-1×10%）=15929元。</p><p><img src=\"http://p1.pstatp.com/large/pgc-image/803976435e6a449288b82630243503f0\" img_width=\"1080\" img_height=\"100\" alt=\"恐慌中，最严国六和新购置税法将在下周共同实施\" inline=\"0\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; border-style: none; max-width: 100%; display: block; margin: 10px auto;\"/></p><p class=\"pgc-img-caption\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); line-height: 16px;\"><br/></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">新购置税法的推出，不仅让消费者的纳税金额更合理，也避免了经销商在交易过程中偷税漏税的行为。不过，新购置税法出台以后，可能很难再享受到类似“购置税减半”优惠政策了。但是从长远来看，这样有利于行业更平稳的发展。</p><p><img src=\"http://p3.pstatp.com/large/pgc-image/042171d822c944f1847862f56b2ca5bc\" img_width=\"1080\" img_height=\"346\" alt=\"恐慌中，最严国六和新购置税法将在下周共同实施\" inline=\"0\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; border-style: none; max-width: 100%; display: block; margin: 10px auto;\"/></p><p class=\"pgc-img-caption\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); line-height: 16px;\"><br/></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">从7月份实施的新政来看，都与消费者的“荷包”息息相关。比如国六标准的来袭，在短时间内势必会增加消费者的购车成本；好在新购置税政策对消费者来说还是比较友好的，至少税费会比之前减少，这相对来说还是个好消息。</p><p><br/></p>',NULL),('9120','<p class=\"ql-align-justify\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: ',NULL),('9160','<p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: \" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" wenquanyi=\"\" micro=\"\" helvetica=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\">40岁的乔布斯在一次接受访谈时表示，“追求极致，分享给同类，这样人类才能共同进步。”</p><p><img src=\"http://p1.pstatp.com/large/pgc-image/52104d95001b44f39bcb644fd8c06042\" img_width=\"800\" img_height=\"594\" alt=\"似疯狂，胜疯狂，与奔驰对标，是WEY追求极致的中式豪华\" inline=\"0\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; border-style: none; max-width: 100%; display: block; margin: 10px auto;\"/></p><p class=\"pgc-img-caption\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); line-height: 16px;\"><br/></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: \" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" wenquanyi=\"\" micro=\"\" helvetica=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\"><br style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box;\"/></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: \" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" wenquanyi=\"\" micro=\"\" helvetica=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\">这并不是乔布斯夸夸其谈，因为他曾为了第一个销售超百亿的爆款——Apple II的箱子设计，而否决了潘通公司提供的超2000种米黄色选择。毫不夸张地说，追求极致是乔布斯时代的苹果能傲视群雄的“无上神功”。</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: \" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" wenquanyi=\"\" micro=\"\" helvetica=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\">1985年4月的张瑞敏收到一封用户投诉海尔冰箱质量问题的信函，在确认仓库里的400多台冰箱中有76台不合格后，抡起大锤将其全部砸毁。在追求极致的理念驱动下，海尔在世界品牌实验室<span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">(World Brand Lab)</span>发布的2018年《中国500最具价值品牌》的报告中，以品牌价值3502.78亿元居第三位。</p><p><img src=\"http://p1.pstatp.com/large/pgc-image/875a5e74681045ffbc21da47f5a24f92\" img_width=\"800\" img_height=\"768\" alt=\"似疯狂，胜疯狂，与奔驰对标，是WEY追求极致的中式豪华\" inline=\"0\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; border-style: none; max-width: 100%; display: block; margin: 10px auto;\"/></p><p class=\"pgc-img-caption\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); line-height: 16px;\"><br/></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: \" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" wenquanyi=\"\" micro=\"\" helvetica=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\"><br style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box;\"/></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: \" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" wenquanyi=\"\" micro=\"\" helvetica=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\">无独有偶，1999年7月时任长安汽车总裁的尹家绪也采取了一次极致的举动，在广场上砸掉了有问题的5辆汽车和10个车身，从此在追求极致产品质量的路上开启了长安在面包车市场的8年黄金期。</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: \" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" wenquanyi=\"\" micro=\"\" helvetica=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\">以上种种，或可表明，企业或品牌在向上发展的过程中，基于正向的市场逻辑<span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">（以消费为导向，有益于发展）</span>，哪怕是采取一些极致的手段或走非寻常的路，也可有利于其脱颖而出。</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: \" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" wenquanyi=\"\" micro=\"\" helvetica=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">01</span></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: \" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" wenquanyi=\"\" micro=\"\" helvetica=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">WEY品牌的极致行为</span></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: \" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" wenquanyi=\"\" micro=\"\" helvetica=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\">当前，车市不确定因素颇多，在合规条件下，企业若敢于突破常规，或也不失为破局的良策。日前，网络上流传一则信息，成立两年多的WEY品牌公然在数十家4S店内的显眼位置各摆出了一台奔驰GLC。据说，此举是为了开展一项名为“WEY式调研”的行动；毫无疑问，这算得上一次疯狂的极致行为。</p><p><img src=\"http://p3.pstatp.com/large/pgc-image/9a4df6cc4e9a4db2a7bb4aea73628406\" img_width=\"800\" img_height=\"526\" alt=\"似疯狂，胜疯狂，与奔驰对标，是WEY追求极致的中式豪华\" inline=\"0\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; border-style: none; max-width: 100%; display: block; margin: 10px auto;\"/></p><p class=\"pgc-img-caption\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); line-height: 16px;\"><br/></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: \" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" wenquanyi=\"\" micro=\"\" helvetica=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\"><br style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box;\"/></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: \" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" wenquanyi=\"\" micro=\"\" helvetica=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\">为什么这么讲？</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: \" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" wenquanyi=\"\" micro=\"\" helvetica=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\">首先，奔驰是豪华车市场的标杆，成立才两年多的WEY品牌为何在公开场合对比标杆？</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: \" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" wenquanyi=\"\" micro=\"\" helvetica=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\">其次，WEY与奔驰的品牌定位不同，为何要让WEY的目标消费者道出二者在产品等方面的差异？</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: \" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" wenquanyi=\"\" micro=\"\" helvetica=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\">最后，奔驰的豪华有目共睹，成立才两年多的WEY品牌何以比对？</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: \" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" wenquanyi=\"\" micro=\"\" helvetica=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\">或许网络上的疑问还不止上述三条，但正如前述种种极端案例，WEY品牌此举或也并非无的放矢，应是一次追求豪华的极致行为。正如佛语有云，种下什么因，就得什么果，一切皆有因缘果报。</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: \" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" wenquanyi=\"\" micro=\"\" helvetica=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">02</span></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: \" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" wenquanyi=\"\" micro=\"\" helvetica=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">WEY品牌要“走上去”，“走出去”</span></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: \" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" wenquanyi=\"\" micro=\"\" helvetica=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\">在去年12月份WEY品牌的两周年之夜上，WEY品牌创始人魏建军发布了WEY品牌的全新战略，他提到，“WEY的品牌取自我的姓氏，我希望，它是名字，更是‘铭志’；而我的志向就是：从‘走上去’，到‘走出去’，把触手可及的豪华带给中国人，把中式当代豪华带到全世界”。</p><p><img src=\"http://p1.pstatp.com/large/pgc-image/be59c09573a649e9b07569d3ae3ca9ac\" img_width=\"800\" img_height=\"361\" alt=\"似疯狂，胜疯狂，与奔驰对标，是WEY追求极致的中式豪华\" inline=\"0\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; border-style: none; max-width: 100%; display: block; margin: 10px auto;\"/></p><p class=\"pgc-img-caption\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); line-height: 16px;\"><br/></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: \" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" wenquanyi=\"\" micro=\"\" helvetica=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\"><br style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box;\"/></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: \" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" wenquanyi=\"\" micro=\"\" helvetica=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\">一定程度上讲，新战略为WEY品牌接下来的行动定了调，其在数十家4S店内摆奔驰GLC也因此有迹可循。</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: \" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" wenquanyi=\"\" micro=\"\" helvetica=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\">若说WEY品牌的“走上去”战略在国内有中式豪华背书，那其“走出去”、让世界认同中式豪华，就必然会面对质疑。</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: \" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" wenquanyi=\"\" micro=\"\" helvetica=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\">毕竟，拥有一百多年历史的奔驰，在全球豪华车市场的地位可以说是出类拔萃，甚至无可撼动。而主打豪华的WEY品牌，在海外豪华车市场就迟早会直面奔驰施加的竞争压力。</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: \" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" wenquanyi=\"\" micro=\"\" helvetica=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\">既然战略已定，消除与奔驰之间的差异，提前做好竞争准备，就成为了WEY品牌眼下该解决的课题。在数十家4S店内摆放奔驰GLC，通过场景化方式开展消费者调研，WEY品牌一方面能找到其在消费者眼中与奔驰的差异，另一方面也可准确地找到其目标消费群体的更真实的需求。由此，这可理解为WEY品牌追求极致豪华的体现，也是其进一步践行“走上去”以及“走出去”的一种体现。</p><p><img src=\"http://p9.pstatp.com/large/pgc-image/070b8487bef749b7a8f9e2dacbf6b8f7\" img_width=\"640\" img_height=\"480\" alt=\"似疯狂，胜疯狂，与奔驰对标，是WEY追求极致的中式豪华\" inline=\"0\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; border-style: none; max-width: 100%; display: block; margin: 10px auto;\"/></p><p class=\"pgc-img-caption\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); line-height: 16px;\"><br/></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: \" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" wenquanyi=\"\" micro=\"\" helvetica=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\"><br style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box;\"/></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: \" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" wenquanyi=\"\" micro=\"\" helvetica=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">03</span></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: \" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" wenquanyi=\"\" micro=\"\" helvetica=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">WEY品牌要有持续差异化的豪华定位</span></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: \" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" wenquanyi=\"\" micro=\"\" helvetica=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\">对标，在汽车行业是很常见的一种手段，基于此能找到与标杆之间的差异、据此提升；但值得注意的是，对标的终极目的不是要做的和标杆雷同甚至一样。大量的营销理论和案例早已证明，差异化的定位是品牌持续发展的基础。</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: \" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" wenquanyi=\"\" micro=\"\" helvetica=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\">诚然，奔驰是豪华车市场的标杆，但豪华车市场也并非只有奔驰一家，擅长驾控的宝马和主打科技的奥迪在豪华车市场同样地位不凡。如前所述，开展“WEY式调研”，WEY品牌既能找到消费者眼中其与奔驰的差异，也能进一步发现目标消费群体眼中的豪华是什么样。</p><p><img src=\"http://p9.pstatp.com/large/pgc-image/1dbb27f2f75c4ccebbd564e63e7a24d7\" img_width=\"693\" img_height=\"1405\" alt=\"似疯狂，胜疯狂，与奔驰对标，是WEY追求极致的中式豪华\" inline=\"0\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; border-style: none; max-width: 100%; display: block; margin: 10px auto;\"/></p><p class=\"pgc-img-caption\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); line-height: 16px;\"><br/></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: \" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" wenquanyi=\"\" micro=\"\" helvetica=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\"><br style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box;\"/></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: \" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" wenquanyi=\"\" micro=\"\" helvetica=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\">WEY品牌在成立之初，提出了差异化的豪华定位，轻奢、安全，是触手可及的豪华，是以安全为基础的豪华。这些与奔驰相比，已然形成了明显的差异化。还是在去年12月份WEY品牌的两周年之夜上，C+智能战略的发布又为WEY品牌的中式豪华加入了新标签。</p><p><img src=\"http://p3.pstatp.com/large/pgc-image/942bd18df5cf4501afbbc94a3b0230bf\" img_width=\"800\" img_height=\"532\" alt=\"似疯狂，胜疯狂，与奔驰对标，是WEY追求极致的中式豪华\" inline=\"0\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; border-style: none; max-width: 100%; display: block; margin: 10px auto;\"/></p><p class=\"pgc-img-caption\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); line-height: 16px;\"><br/></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: \" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" wenquanyi=\"\" micro=\"\" helvetica=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\"><br style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box;\"/></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: \" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" wenquanyi=\"\" micro=\"\" helvetica=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\">事实上，在与奔驰GLC的同台比对中，WEY品牌旗下旗舰燃油车型VV7体现了这种差异化的豪华定位，以及对极致产品的追求。</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: \" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" wenquanyi=\"\" micro=\"\" helvetica=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\">首先，VV7的价格就体现了与奔驰的差异化，16.98-18.88万元的指导价显然比39.08-56.28万元更触手可及；</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: \" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" wenquanyi=\"\" micro=\"\" helvetica=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\">其次，奔驰GLC的外观自然是大气豪华的，但VV7偏运动化的外观设计，也体现了对年轻消费群体的照顾；</p><p><img src=\"http://p1.pstatp.com/large/pgc-image/6a5e5b8eb9cd418088ad25b91bc09fb5\" img_width=\"800\" img_height=\"532\" alt=\"似疯狂，胜疯狂，与奔驰对标，是WEY追求极致的中式豪华\" inline=\"0\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; border-style: none; max-width: 100%; display: block; margin: 10px auto;\"/></p><p class=\"pgc-img-caption\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); line-height: 16px;\"><br/></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: \" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" wenquanyi=\"\" micro=\"\" helvetica=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\"><br style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box;\"/></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: \" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" wenquanyi=\"\" micro=\"\" helvetica=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\">再次，与奔驰GLC相比，VV7的内饰设计在视觉上的豪华感有可比性；</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: \" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" wenquanyi=\"\" micro=\"\" helvetica=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\">最后，VV7丰富的智能化应用则是奔驰GLC所不完全具备的，比如ACC全速范围自适应巡航功能、AEB主动式紧急制动系统、ICA智能巡航辅助+TJA交通拥堵辅助、LCK车道居中保持辅助系统+LKA车道保持辅助系统+LDW车道偏离预警+道路交通标识识别等。</p><p><img src=\"http://p1.pstatp.com/large/pgc-image/bc122b90643b43899584172580b98117\" img_width=\"800\" img_height=\"533\" alt=\"似疯狂，胜疯狂，与奔驰对标，是WEY追求极致的中式豪华\" inline=\"0\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; border-style: none; max-width: 100%; display: block; margin: 10px auto;\"/></p><p class=\"pgc-img-caption\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); line-height: 16px;\"><br/></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: \" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" wenquanyi=\"\" micro=\"\" helvetica=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\"><br style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box;\"/></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: \" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" wenquanyi=\"\" micro=\"\" helvetica=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\">而这一次的“WEY式调研”后，WEY品牌将有机会进一步优化完善其差异化的豪华品牌定位。</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: \" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" wenquanyi=\"\" micro=\"\" helvetica=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">04</span></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: \" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" wenquanyi=\"\" micro=\"\" helvetica=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">WEY品牌有“走上去”、“走出去”的基础</span></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: \" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" wenquanyi=\"\" micro=\"\" helvetica=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\">抛开前述网络上可能存在的质疑，WEY品牌这次公开的对标奔驰，也并非没有底气。</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: \" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" wenquanyi=\"\" micro=\"\" helvetica=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\">且不论品牌成立两年后累计销量即超过26万辆，在短时间内即完成价位不同、产品定位不同、动力不同的VV7、VV5、VV6、P8四款车型布局，单单说WEY品牌在“做豪华”这件工作上就是做足了准备的。</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: \" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" wenquanyi=\"\" micro=\"\" helvetica=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\">首先，如前所述，品牌战略及发展思路很清晰，不仅是第一个中国豪华品牌，还是第一个走出去的中国豪华品牌。</p><p><img src=\"http://p1.pstatp.com/large/pgc-image/fe17e23f873f4d6e8449b84b12f1068a\" img_width=\"640\" img_height=\"480\" alt=\"似疯狂，胜疯狂，与奔驰对标，是WEY追求极致的中式豪华\" inline=\"0\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; border-style: none; max-width: 100%; display: block; margin: 10px auto;\"/></p><p class=\"pgc-img-caption\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); line-height: 16px;\"><br/></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: \" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" wenquanyi=\"\" micro=\"\" helvetica=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\">其次，在研发能力上准备充分。公开资料显示，WEY品牌在成立之初就组建了由来自宝马、奥迪等豪华品牌的资深专家组成的设计、研发团队。除在德国之外，WEY品牌在日本、美国、印度、奥地利、韩国等设立了海外研发中心，完成全球研发体系布局。</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: \" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" wenquanyi=\"\" micro=\"\" helvetica=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\">2017年9月，WEY参展法兰克福车展，VV5与保时捷911 GT3、奥迪AICON概念车、Smart EQ概念车等共同被德国三大新闻周刊之一的《Focus》评为“法兰克福车展最成功的五大车型”，向欧洲消费者展示了WEY品牌的中式豪华。</p><p><img src=\"http://p3.pstatp.com/large/pgc-image/8f2d44794d8540aaa72984a88f2b72dc\" img_width=\"800\" img_height=\"473\" alt=\"似疯狂，胜疯狂，与奔驰对标，是WEY追求极致的中式豪华\" inline=\"0\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; border-style: none; max-width: 100%; display: block; margin: 10px auto;\"/></p><p class=\"pgc-img-caption\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); line-height: 16px;\"><br/></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: \" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" wenquanyi=\"\" micro=\"\" helvetica=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\"><br style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box;\"/></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: \" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" wenquanyi=\"\" micro=\"\" helvetica=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">写在最后：</span>从一开始，中国品牌向上进入豪华车市场，就是破局之举，这一定程度上注定了中国豪华品牌要走不寻常的发展之路。WEY品牌此次开展的“WEY式调研”，初一看来的确是一种极致行为，但如前所述整体来看，却也是合情合理之举。常言道，“不疯魔不成活”，中国豪华品牌或就需要一些“疯狂”，才能打造极致的豪华品牌。</p><p><br/></p>',NULL);
